ActHistoric Sites and Monuments Act
PrecisReappointment of LORNE WHEELER of St. John's, Newfoundland and Labrador, as a member of the Historic Sites and Monuments Board of Canada, as a representative of the Province of Newfoundland and Labrador, to hold office during pleasure for a period of four years, effective June 18, 2013.
